
VERSIONING/VERSIONS 

  version 1 will be...
  version 2 will be... etc

  could do a table

  what and why is important 

  version 1 needs to start with the database because everything else runs off the database. its the backbone. 

  version 1  needs user registration 
  
  version 1 is the pure essential your system cant exist without. 
  
  version 2 - login, bookings, cancellations STUFF THE SYSTEM MUST DO 
  
  version 3 - altering appointments, branding, audit, css NICE TO HAVES, BELLS AND WHISTLES 
  
  can do more then 3 but need at least 3 


